Loicque Hello,

Back in 2018 we made some transfers in PLN for purchases of shares in a
private company.

When I try to find them online they are not visible on the 'Transactions'
tab, as all transactions prior to Jan 2019 are referred to the 'Documents'
tab.

However, on the Documents tab, I can only find the USD-to-PLN conversions
that were made ahead of the PLN transfers, but not the transfers themselves.

Is there any way to get at this historical information?

Thanks,

Adam

